questions.text:
Match the Xenon compounds listed in Column I with their corresponding molecular geometries/shapes listed in Column II, and choose the correct option based on the VSEPR theory as applied to Group 18 elements.

 egin{itemize}
    \item[Column I:] (A) $XeF_4$, (B) $XeF_6$, (C) $XeOF_4$, (D) $XeO_3$
    \item[Column II:] (p) Pyramidal, (q) Square Planar, (r) Distorted Octahedral, (s) Square Pyramidal
\end{itemize}
